        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Save Rural Hospitals Act of </b><b>2021</b></p> <p>This bill establishes an area wage adjustment floor for Medicare hospital payments in states that are not frontier states and excludes such adjustments from certain budget neutrality rules.</p>]]>
        </text>
